product_description: This Samsung RT65B7058BS Smart Convertible 5-in-1 Refrigerator with the help of Twin Cooling Plus Technology offers five different mode options to convert the refrigerator according to your storage requirement i.e., normal mode, extra fridge mode, seasonal mode, vacation mode and home alone mode. The Twin Cooling Plus Technology controls the refrigerator and freezer independently with two separate fans that in turn provides ideal temperature, humidity preservation, superior energy saving and also prevents mixing of odours. The normal mode is best for your normal daily usage to keep the food fresh for long and to make ice faster. When you have bought lot many groceries from the super market, you can switch to the extra fridge mode which helps you in converting the freezer into fridge for more organized storage. Switch to seasonal mode when the season changes, this mode put the freezer off and keep the refrigerator off and contributes for energy savings. The vacation mode keeps the freezer on and puts off the refrigerator and it is the perfect mode when you are going out on a vacation and you want to store some food in the freezer. The home alone mode switches of the refrigerator compartment and converts the freezer into refrigerator and it is the best mode when you are alone at home and you don t have lot to store. In addition to this, the refrigerator flaunts an easy clean black inox door with a bar handle that is quiet easy to clean and also adds a classy touch to your home interior.
